{"tid":748764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【改詞MV】2018年世界盃回顧歌曲","createTime":"2018-07-19T12:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T01:04:56.000Z","uid":37464,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6068e89cb013a045d5e2e08841f25fbadeff0477","tid":748764,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/L0RLXI5_x2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL0RLXI5_x2s&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bb453f9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/L0RLXI5_x2s</a><br />\n<br />\n原詞：黃偉文<br />\n作曲：Edmond Tsang@阿房宮<br />\n填詞：DC_<br />\n演唱：柒菇碌叔叔 <br />\n原曲 : 不同班同學<br />\n<br />\n開場前一刻<br />\n誰人猜想過結局會離奇怪誕<br />\n強如德軍保守到竟然未可出線便折返<br />\n毫無餘力似卡雲尼去感嘆<br />\n而或許摩洛哥到最後還未慣<br />\n勝負也需要靠運　彷如人生好比伊朗　<br />\n追平卻恨晚<br />\n<br />\n於埋門一刻<br />\n如俄軍比分優勢沒人能想像嗎<br />\n南韓力盡想毅然回家　接應卻是傻瓜<br />\n熱愛拋雞蛋恭候嗎<br />\n何妨嘗試像比鄰攜鮮花<br />\n夾道裡因有入球已夠慶祝一晚<br />\n球員付上力氣為了甚麼　能答謝嗎<br />\n<br />\n中場時一刻<br />\n來源非洲那國度叫旁人慨嘆<br />\n就在搶分的一戰　不斷掉失分數服氣嗎<br />\n而神奇在阿根廷能夠反勝<br />\n還是始於敵不過後防如敗瓦<br />\n較弱勢小國縱是中段敗走<br />\n北歐諸國　也算踢得優雅<br />\n<br />\n當完場一刻<br />\n前場消遣的島國奪回人心是嗎<br />\n悠長平局中　歷來唯一　決賽這樣來嗎<br />\n讓格仔軍編寫神話<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙靠著一人成軍嗎<br />\n勝利裡少有入球以配搭給轉化<br />\n狂牛換帥　換上舊有臉譜　賠了代價<br />\n<br />\n意外裡傷勢復發　最後要觀看國家隊搏殺<br />\n沒有一絲對策　就算不甘也要認了嗎<br />\n<br />\n而龍門各自補城牆一刻<br />\n頑強將巴西阻隔後來才滾地吵架<br />\n瀕臨絕境中煉成紅魔　奮戰勇奪成果<br />\n就似英軍將咒語下了架<br />\n<br />\n人才如法裔超豪華餐單<br />\n放在了今屆陣容　哪個夠他搶眼<br />\n誰人漸老沒法下屆復返<br />\n遺留在世靜看後上之秀　能夠耀眼"},{"pid":"7b440f828fcd5ba91538590a9bb881fb9b956b4e","tid":748764,"uid":37464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"歷年國際大賽回顧：<br />\n2018年外圍賽：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/EM_KhIEzzmA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEM_KhIEzzmA&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c152375d\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/EM_KhIEzzmA</a><br />\n2016年歐國盃：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/yRk3on6Z4MY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyRk3on6Z4MY&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0e825030\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/yRk3on6Z4MY</a><br />\n2014年世界盃：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/LqLo1hrIumo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLqLo1hrIumo&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6e225969\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/LqLo1hrIumo</a><br />\n2012年歐國盃：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/AlHedumuyHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAlHedumuyHg&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=383a85fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/AlHedumuyHg</a><br />\n2006年世界盃：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/T_SFqaPnEcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT_SFqaPnEcI&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6abc0926\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/T_SFqaPnEcI</a>"},{"pid":"d85066edda394caa431635a628cac528081460b5","tid":748764,"uid":138218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"支持!!"},{"pid":"29ad297214bd3968d7f6e5317d1f38ad918bbcf1","tid":748764,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"以為譚校長果首改編添"},{"pid":"698a405ea5b9fc2c94377385b04407a0d347db9d","tid":748764,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85066edda394caa431635a628cac528081460b5","tid":748764,"uid":138218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"支持!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f9592c6b6bcbd6025e67ecf6bcb9abdc839093","tid":748764,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ad297214bd3968d7f6e5317d1f38ad918bbcf1","tid":748764,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"以為譚校長果首改編添"},"citedBy":